---
title: Quick-Marinated Steak with Orange-Balsamic-Roasted Veggies
description: Rosemary, orange, garlic and balsamic vinegar team up for a winning marinade in this weeknight steak dinner. The key to these veggies is caramelization—don’t take them out of the oven until they’re nice and golden brown!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-marinated-steak-324a4e45.jpg
